id.co.veritrans.mdk.v1.gateway.model

Class VtResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • id.co.veritrans.mdk.v1.gateway.model.VtResponse

  • public class VtResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Veritrans API response. Every response returned by Veritrans Payment API is represented by this class. Generally one must check the statusCode property to reliably determine the result of a request, do not ever rely on the HTTP status code.
